headline: Kewaunee Scientific Announces Appointment of J. Jette Campbell to Board of Directors
summary: Kewaunee Scientific Corporation (NASDAQ: KEQU), a recognized leader in the design, manufacture, and installation of laboratory, healthcare, and technical furniture products, announces the appointment of J. Jette Campbell, CPA, to its Board of Directors, effective September 10, 2025.
